extends ../main

block content

  h1(style="margin-bottom: 30px") You Subscribed

  p Hey #{ user.profile.name },

  p You are now subscribed to updates for - <a style="color: #0B9BD0" href="#{ url }/idea/#{ idea._id }/info">#{ idea.title }</a>.

  p We will let you know when interesting things happen like people ask questions in the design area or you receive replies to your comments.

  p If you no longer want to receive updates from this idea then just visit the idea page <a style="color: #0B9BD0" href="#{ url }/idea/#{ idea._id }/info">here</a> and unsubscribe.